==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mogul empire
<hw>Mo*gul" empire</hw></mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Mogul</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>.]</ety> <def>The empire created in
<country>India</country> by invading Mongolians (Tatars), established
under <persfn>Baber</persfn>, who conquered Hindustan in 1526. The
established religion of the empire was Islam. After the death of the
Great Mogul <persfn>Aurung-Zeb</persfn> in 1707, power passed to the
Mahrattas and the British. The empire existed only nominally in the
early 1800's, and was finally abolished in 1857 by the deposing of the
last emperor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Moha</ent>⟦br⟧
